    <dl class="tabs">
      <dd class="active"><a href="#list">School Closing List</a></dd>
      <dd><a href="#map">Map</a></dd>
    </dl>
    <ul class="tabs-content">
      <li class="active" id="listTab">
        <table class="twelve">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Name</th>
              <th>Address</th>
              <th>Foo</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>

          <% @schools.each do |school| %>
            <tr>
              <td><%= school.name.titleize %></td>
              <td><%= school.address.titleize %></td>
              <td><%= link_to 'Show', school %></td>
            </tr>
          <% end %>

        </table>
      </li>
      <li id="mapTab">This is simple tab 2s content. Now you see it!</li>
    </ul>

  </div>

  <div class="six columns">
    <div id="news">
      <h4>Recent News</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>NewsWorks: <a href="http://www.newsworks.org/index.php/the-feed/item/52119-what-should-become-of-the-germantown-high-school-property">What should become of the Germantown High School property?</a>, 3/11/2013</li>
    </div>

    <div id="resources">
      <h4>Resources</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://www.pewtrusts.org/uploadedFiles/wwwpewtrustsorg/Reports/Philadelphia_Research_Initiative/Philadelphia-School-Closings.pdf">Pew: Shuttered Public Schools: The Struggle to Bring Old Buildings New Life</a>, 2/11/2013</li>
        <li><a href="http://www.pewtrusts.org/uploadedFiles/wwwpewtrustsorg/Reports/Philadelphia_Research_Initiative/Closing-Public-Schools-Philadelphia.pdf">Closing Public Schools in Philadelphia: Lessons from Six Urban Districts</a>, 10/19/2011</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div id="data-sources">
      <h6>Data Sources</h6>
      <p>School location and demographic information is available as part of the School District's <a href="http://webgui.phila.k12.pa.us/offices/a/accountability/open-data-initiative">Open Data Initiative</a>. The listing of schools to be closed can be found on the School District's <a href="http://webgui.phila.k12.pa.us/offices/f/facilities-master-plan">Facilities Master Plan</a>.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>